[SN]TITLE[SN]
Lorry fire causes Lanarkshire motorway closure

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A carriageway of one of Scotland's busiest sections of motorway has been closed due to a lorry fire.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The Edinburgh to Glasgow M8 motorway has been closed westbound between junction 5 (Harthill) and junction 6 (Newhouse).
Alternative routes through North Lanarkshire are expected to be extremely busy.
There are no reports of any injuries in the fire.
